query:
SELECT wl.id, wl.studentId, wl.status, wl.trainingDate, wl.totalSets, wl.totalReps, wl.totalVolume, wl.totalDuration, wl.feeling
FROM workout_logs wl
ORDER BY wl.id DESC
LIMIT 10
